--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project depends on, and — via the prebuilt runtime bundle the CLI ships —
redistributes, the following third-party software. Each retains its own
copyright and license; consult the respective package for full terms.

  - liveline (liveline@0.0.7) — MIT — live price-chart engine; vendored with a
    local patch for retina rendering and axis-label precision
    (see patches/liveline@0.0.7.patch).
  - gridstack — MIT — drag/resize grid layout powering the editable dashboard.
  - zod — MIT — schema definitions and dashboard.json validation.
  - d3, d3-hierarchy — ISC — chart math and layout.
  - Unicorn Studio engine (unicornStudio.umd.mjs) — proprietary, © Unicorn
    Studio (https://github.com/hiunicornstudio/unicornstudio.js; use granted
    for integration with Unicorn Studio projects) — the optional animated
    background. A copy of the publicly distributed web-embed engine is
    self-hosted in the prebuilt runtime and used only to render Unicorn
    Studio-hosted scenes.
  - react, react-dom — MIT — bundled into the prebuilt runtime the CLI serves.
